steps.name: Open METCAL Runtime and enter valid login and password for MC user
Click on the LogIn button
Select Configure then Instrument Control section and verify APPLY and DISCARD buttons are disabled
Move IEEE-488 FIND LISTENER Delay slider to the 300 ms value
Verify Yellow banner is popUp
Verify APPLY and DISCARD button is enabled
Verify value is changed for IEEE-488 FIND LISTENER Delay slider
Click DISCARD button AND assert confirmation message "Are you sure you want to discard your changes?"

arguments.val: "Are you sure you want to discard your changes?"

steps.name: Click Yes on confirmation message and assert APPLY and Discard button is disabled
Move IEEE488 FIND LISTENER Delay slider to the 400 ms value
Verify Yellow banner is popUp
Verify APPLY and DISCARD button is enabled
Click APPLY button
Verify APPLY and DISCARD button is disabled
Verify value is changed for IEEE-488 FIND LISTENER Delay slider
Change location of the IEEE-488 FIND LISTENER Delay slider to original and click APPLY
Move IEEE2/SCPI Query Delay slider to the 420 ms value
Verify Yellow banner is popUp
Verify APPLY and DISCARD button is enabled
Verify value is changed for IEEE2/SCPI Query Delay slider
Click DISCARD button AND assert confirmation message "Are you sure you want to discard your changes?"

arguments.val: "Are you sure you want to discard your changes?"
